OL,3,CEuropean cities UK holidaymakers 'most
OL,4,Cwant to visit' in 2026 revealed
OL,6,FMore than half (56%) of holidaymakers
OL,7,Fplan to travel more often in 2026 `
OL,8,Fbut many are looking to trim their
OL,9,Fbudgets, a survey of city break
OL,10,Ftravellers indicates.
OL,12,FLocation often takes priority over
OL,13,Fluxury when choosing a place to stay,
OL,14,Fthe research found.
OL,16,FThe survey was carried out in
OL,17,FDecember, among 2,000 people who had
OL,18,Ftaken a European city break in the
OL,19,Fpast 12 months or who plan to go on a
OL,20,FEuropean city break in the coming 12
OL,21,Fmonths.
