OL,3,CEuropean cities UK holidaymakers 'most
OL,4,Cwant to visit' in 2026 revealed
OL,6,FWhen asked about choosing
OL,7,Faccommodation for city breaks, 71% of
OL,8,Fholidaymakers said a prime city centre
OL,9,Flocation is critical, while 7% would
OL,10,Fprioritise luxury facilities, 9% would
OL,11,Ffavour on-site food and drink and 7%
OL,12,Fwould look for gyms and fitness
OL,13,Famenities.
OL,15,FNearly a third (29%) of holidaymakers
OL,16,Fexpect to reduce their overall spend
OL,17,Fon European city breaks next year,
OL,18,Fwhile 9% plan to spend more, according
OL,19,Fto the survey carried out for pan
OL,20,FEuropean hostel operator Safestay.
