OL,3,CEuropean cities UK holidaymakers 'most
OL,4,Cwant to visit' in 2026 revealed
OL,6,FAsked what made their favourite
OL,7,FEuropean city break memorable, nearly
OL,8,Fa fifth (18%) of people said great
OL,9,Flocal food and drink while 15%
OL,10,Fhighlighted the people they travelled
OL,11,Fwith.
OL,13,FLooking ahead, Prague and Copenhagen
OL,14,Fjointly topped the list of European
OL,15,Fcities that UK holidaymakers most want
OL,16,Fto visit in 2026 (17%), ahead of
OL,17,FVenice (14%), Athens (14%), Barcelona
OL,18,F(13%) and Paris (13%), according to
OL,19,Fthe survey, carried out by Find Out
OL,20,FNow.
