OL,3,CEuropean cities UK holidaymakers 'most
OL,4,Cwant to visit' in 2026 revealed
OL,6,FPeter Zielke, chief operating officer
OL,7,Fof Safestay, said: "This research
OL,8,Fhighlights a clear shift in how people
OL,9,Fare thinking about city breaks.
OL,11,F"Travellers prioritising experiences
OL,12,Fover fills and are becoming much more
OL,13,Fdeliberate about where they spend
OL,14,Ftheir money ` with being right in the
OL,15,Fheart of a city, close to the culture,
OL,16,Ffood and attractions the most
OL,17,Fimportant factor."
